column3: For the years ended June 30, 2020 (“fiscal 2020”), June 30, 2019 (“fiscal 2019”), and June 30, 2018 (“fiscal 2018”), Professional Employer Organization (“PEO”) revenues are net of direct pass-through costs, primarily consisting of payroll wages and payroll taxes, of $45,826.1 million, $42,688.8 million, and $39,140.9 million, respectively.
